items.headline: Delicious ready made meals for week 36

recipe.name: Smoky Chicken Fajitas
recipe.headline: with Sour Cream, Peppers, and Onion
recipe.descriptionMarkdown: Lime crema gives these fajitas a zesty finish that will keep you coming back for more.  With the perfect blend of spices, roasted peppers and onions, melted cheese, and fluffy flour tortillas, you will need to eat them quickly before someone else does...

Each meal serves 1 adult or 1-2 children
